GetTeam1.prototype = Object.extendsObject(global.AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
GetTeam: function()
		{
	gs.info("id:- "+gs.getUserID());
	var rec = new GlideRecord('x_568702_birthday_birthday');
	rec.addQuery('u_name', gs.getUserID());
	rec.query();
	var team = [];
	while(rec.next())
		{

		}
	gs.info("team:- "+team);
	return team;
},
